{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/wu-yi-gong-di-wei-dang-sheng-ji-tui-xing-zhi-wu-qiang-wei-dang-ying-lu-se-jun-yun/","webpackCompilationHash":"c05de8f8e24aa66aa83f","result":{"data":{"ghostPost":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d11c57295f47f3656854183","title":"武汉工地围挡升级：推行植物墙围挡，迎“绿色军运”","slug":"wu-yi-gong-di-wei-dang-sheng-ji-tui-xing-zhi-wu-qiang-wei-dang-ying-lu-se-jun-yun","featured":true,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/2-2.jpg","excerpt":"武汉正在开展工地围挡提档升级计划。新开工地都将使用绿植围挡，并结合周边环境采用园林式围挡。","custom_excerpt":"武汉正在开展工地围挡提档升级计划。新开工地都将使用绿植围挡，并结合周边环境采用园林式围挡。","created_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","published_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"08 July, 2019","created_at":"2019-06-25T14:55:46.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-06-25T14:57:30.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-07-08T11:19:21.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"}],"primary_author":{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"},"primary_tag":{"name":"建筑绿化","slug":"jianzhu-lu-hua","description":"建筑绿化、垂直绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"建筑绿化","slug":"jianzhu-lu-hua","description":"建筑绿化、垂直绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"}],"plaintext":"武汉正在开展工地围挡提档升级计划。新开工地都将使用绿植围挡，并结合周边环境采用园林式围挡。目前以完成围挡绿化的有博物馆对面的青年路段。\n\n青年路的围挡绿化升级后，周围工地外的绿植围挡铺满了新鲜的绿植并与周围的道路景观融为一体。整体效果显得绿色、自然赏心悦目。\n\n整个围挡围挡共有308㎡\n。围挡改造从11月中旬开始动工，目前以处于完工状态。据施工方负责人介绍，绿植围挡步骤主要分成测算尺寸、制作效果图、搭建刚建构、底盒安装、绿植安装、水电安装、灌溉系统安装、灯饰与广告字等......\n\n绿植围挡从外观上看拥有鲜明的质感与美感。翠绿的植物墙景观效果强，色彩层次鲜明。在实际的应用中，它能起到降尘减噪的作用减少了工地施工所带来的环境污染与噪音污染。其支撑点选用的钢结构，整体抗压性强，整体的使用年限最少可达10年之久。","html":"<p>武汉正在开展工地围挡提档升级计划。新开工地都将使用绿植围挡，并结合周边环境采用园林式围挡。目前以完成围挡绿化的有博物馆对面的青年路段。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>青年路的围挡绿化升级后，周围工地外的绿植围挡铺满了新鲜的绿植并与周围的道路景观融为一体。整体效果显得绿色、自然赏心悦目。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/2.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/3-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>整个围挡围挡共有308㎡ 。围挡改造从11月中旬开始动工，目前以处于完工状态。据施工方负责人介绍，绿植围挡步骤主要分成测算尺寸、制作效果图、搭建刚建构、底盒安装、绿植安装、水电安装、灌溉系统安装、灯饰与广告字等......</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/6.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>绿植围挡从外观上看拥有鲜明的质感与美感。翠绿的植物墙景观效果强，色彩层次鲜明。在实际的应用中，它能起到降尘减噪的作用减少了工地施工所带来的环境污染与噪音污染。其支撑点选用的钢结构，整体抗压性强，整体的使用年限最少可达10年之久。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/7.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/07/8.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image-->","url":"https://new.a-green.cn/wu-yi-gong-di-wei-dang-sheng-ji-tui-xing-zhi-wu-qiang-wei-dang-ying-lu-se-jun-yun/","uuid":"ca11b9e8-ba5e-4c8d-bd44-8b6f6a3a57c2","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5d11c57295f47f3656854183"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"wu-yi-gong-di-wei-dang-sheng-ji-tui-xing-zhi-wu-qiang-wei-dang-ying-lu-se-jun-yun"}}}